AcscBranchFaultImpl
public class AcscBusFaultImpl
extends AcscBusRefImpl
implements AcscBusFault

An implementation of the model object 'Bus Fault'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Fault Type
  • Fault Code
  • ZLG Fault
  • ZLL Fault
  • Fault Result
